iana.encoding_considerations:
Security considerations: This media type is not expected to contain any active or executable content. Information contained in application/vnd.vocalshaper.vsp4 documents may contains user names(When the user has not enabled anonymous mode in the VocalShaper application for saving documents), document creation time and document latest modification time.

Interoperability considerations: None.

Published specification: The data in application/vnd.vocalshaper.vsp4 documents is defined based on the .proto files in the following link:
https://github.com/Do-sth-sharp/VocalShaperProject4/tree/main/proto

Applications which use this media: VocalShaper, The Open Source Digital Audio Workstation.
https://github.com/Do-sth-sharp/VocalShaper

Fragment identifier considerations: N/A

Restrictions on usage: The application/vnd.vocalshaper.vsp4 documents are only used to save VocalShaper application project data. And for exchanging project data with other applications.
